      "y": 850,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• Relocate essential loads to (N) Protected Load Panel; balance phases to MSP."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 860,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• Test Edison-style 240V circuits before commissioning; verify L1/L2 polarity."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 870,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• 10–12 single-pole loads max on PLP; 240V loads consume two slots."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 880,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• Duracell battery floor-mounted on rigid rack; min 36\" front clearance."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 890,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• Heat detectors required in conditioned battery room (NEC 706.5 / IFC 1207)."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 850,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• Bollards 3' min height in front of exterior battery enclosure."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 860,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• CT extension kit P/N 1001808 with #18 AWG shielded cable, 100' max run."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 870,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• #18 AWG shielded twisted pair for all RGM telemetry; bond shield at gateway."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 880,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• MSP upgrade to 225A required if existing busbar < 200A continuous."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 390,
      "y": 890,
      "fontSize": 7.5,
      "color": "#a00",
      "text": "• Smoke detectors and CO sensors required per local AHJ for indoor battery."
